### Phase 13: Frontend Design Overhaul 🎨 (HIGHEST PRIORITY — spawn Frontend then Polish)

This phase completely re-skins the frontend to match premium mockup images. The current frontend is architecturally sound but visually basic — it needs to look like Nike, Instagram, TripAdvisor, and Airbnb.

**CRITICAL READING ORDER FOR ALL PHASE 13 AGENTS:**
1. `C:\Users\dongu\atlas\atlas-assets\DESIGN-SPEC.md` — the authoritative visual design specification
2. All mockup images in `C:\Users\dongu\atlas\atlas-assets\mockups\` (01-07)
3. `C:\Users\dongu\atlas\atlas-assets\design-tokens.css` — CSS custom properties

